title: Affinity Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Raw, Thai, Western, Juice bar, Bakery
description: Vegetarian cafe with many vegan and gluten free options. In-house-made cakes and specialty raw vegan tart are menu items. Drinks include coffees, cold pressed juices and pea protein shakes. Different oriental delight daily and vegan soups.
